snippet.title: RUMBLE - VR Earthbending Fighting Game [RELEASE TRAILER]
snippet.description:
Are you ready to RUMBLE?! It's now available on Steam, go check it out: https://store.steampowered.com/app/890550/RUMBLE/

RUMBLE is a Virtual Reality fighting game, that's played without pressing buttons. By learning to perform specific motions, you can both attack your opponent and defend yourself!

Join our Discord to chat with other players: https://discord.gg/rSaTNYU4CF
